The paper deals with automatic facial expression recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach uses deep neural networks, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the proposed approach is in human-computer interaction systems, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper deals with visual information, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
